        "title": "feat(i18n): translate Nodes page UI strings to Simplified Chinese",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\n- Problem: Nodes page (`/nodes`) had extensive hardcoded English strings in the `nodes` namespace of `zh-CN.ts` (historical omission) and the entire `nodes-exec-approvals.ts` sub-component was not internationalized at all.\r\n- Why it matters: Non-English users see English labels throughout the Nodes page — exec approvals panel, node bindings, device lists, token actions, and pairing statuses.\r\n- What changed: Filled all missing `nodes.*` translations in `zh-CN.ts`. Added new `execApprovalsConfig` keys to both `en.ts` and `zh-CN.ts`. Extracted all hardcoded strings from `nodes-exec-approvals.ts` into `t()` calls, replacing inline `SECURITY_OPTIONS`/`ASK_OPTIONS` labels with `getSecurityLabel()` / `getAskLabel()` helpers for runtime localization.\r\n- What did NOT change (scope boundary): No functional behavior, logic, or styling changed. No new features added. Node IDs and gateway names remain in English. No other locales touched beyond the standard i18n sync cascade.\r\n\r\n## Change Type (select all)\r\n\r\n- [ ] Bug fix\r\n- [ ] Feature\r\n- [ ] Refactor required for the fix\r\n- [ ] Docs\r\n- [x] Chore/infra\r\n\r\n## Scope (select all touched areas)\r\n\r\n- [ ] Gateway / orchestration\r\n- [ ] Skills / tool execution\r\n- [ ] Auth / tokens\r\n- [ ] Memory / storage\r\n- [ ] Integrations\r\n- [ ] API / contracts\r\n- [x] UI / DX\r\n- [ ] CI/CD / infra\r\n\r\n## Linked Issue/PR\r\n\r\n- Closes #\r\n- Related #\r\n- [ ] This PR fixes a bug or regression\r\n\r\n## Real behavior proof (required for external PRs)\r\n\r\n- Behavior or issue addressed: Nodes page UI strings were not fully localized to Simplified Chinese; `nodes-exec-approvals.ts` was entirely un-internationalized.\r\n- Real environment tested: Local dev gateway (`pnpm gateway:dev`).\r\n- Exact steps or command run after this patch: Built UI assets with `pnpm build`, started gateway, opened Control UI Nodes tab.\r\n- Evidence after fix: Screenshot — exec approvals panel shows Chinese labels for target, security mode, ask policy, ask fallback, auto-allow skill CLIs, and allowlist sections.\r\n- Observed result after fix: zh-CN locale shows fully translated Nodes page UI.\r\n- What was not tested: Other non-English locales.\r\n\r\nbefore\r\n<img width=\"2922\" height=\"1714\" alt=\"6\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/cfab0703-9708-467f-aec7-52c44ea17c4a\" />\r\n\r\nafter\r\n<img width=\"2916\" height=\"1448\" alt=\"7\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6c57aa07-f776-41e2-b6fb-559f822cf940\" />\r\n\r\n\r\n## Root Cause (if applicable)\r\n\r\nN/A — not a bug fix.\r\n\r\n## Regression Test Plan (if applicable)\r\n\r\nN/A — not a bug fix or regression.\r\n\r\n## User-visible / Behavior Changes\r\n\r\n- Nodes page title, subtitle, device list, pairing statuses, token actions, and node bindings now fully localized to Simplified Chinese (zh-CN).\r\n- Exec approvals panel (target selection, security mode, ask policy, ask fallback, auto-allow skill CLIs, allowlist) now fully localized to Simplified Chinese.\r\n- Dropdown options for security mode (deny/allowlist/full) and ask policy (off/on-miss/always) now display in Chinese.\r\n- English locale unchanged (new keys added, existing behavior preserved).\r\n\r\n## Diagram (if applicable)\r\n\r\nN/A\r\n\r\n## Security Impact (required)\r\n\r\n- New permissions/capabilities? (`No`)\r\n- Secrets/tokens handling changed? (`No`)\r\n- New/changed network calls? (`No`)\r\n- Command/tool execution surface changed? (`No`)\r\n- Data access scope changed? (`No`)\r\n- If any `Yes`, explain risk + mitigation:\r\n\r\n## Repro + Verification\r\n\r\n### Environment\r\n\r\n- OS: macOS\r\n- Runtime/container: Node 22 (local dev)\r\n- Model/provider: N/A\r\n- Integration/channel (if any): N/A\r\n- Relevant config (redacted): N/A\r\n\r\n### Steps\r\n\r\n1. `pnpm build` to build Control UI assets\r\n2. `pnpm gateway:dev` to start local gateway\r\n3. Open Control UI in browser, navigate to Nodes tab\r\n4. Switch locale to zh-CN (if not already)\r\n5. Observe exec approvals panel labels, dropdown options, and node bindings\r\n6. Scroll to device list and verify pairing status labels\r\n\r\n### Expected\r\n\r\n- Exec approvals title: \"Exec 审批\"\r\n- Target section: \"目标\", \"主机\", \"节点\"\r\n- Security mode dropdown: \"拒绝\", \"允许列表\", \"完全允许\"\r\n- Ask policy dropdown: \"关闭\", \"缺失时\", \"始终\"\r\n- Ask fallback dropdown: \"拒绝\", \"允许列表\", \"完全允许\"\r\n- Auto-allow skill CLIs: \"自动允许技能 CLI\", \"已启用\"\r\n- Node bindings: \"默认绑定\", \"任意节点\", \"使用默认值\"\r\n- Device list: \"设备\", \"没有已配对设备。\"\r\n\r\n### Actual\r\n\r\n- All above verified locally.\r\n\r\n## Evidence\r\n\r\n- [ ] Failing test/log before + passing after\r\n- [ ] Trace/log snippets\r\n- [x] Screenshot/recording (to be added by reviewer)\r\n- [ ] Perf numbers (if relevant)\r\n\r\n**Before**\r\nTODO: Screenshot to be added by reviewer.\r\n\r\n**After**\r\nTODO: Screenshot to be added by reviewer.\r\n\r\n## Human Verification (required)\r\n\r\n- Verified scenarios: Nodes tab exec approvals panel, node bindings, device list, and pairing statuses in zh-CN locale.\r\n- Edge cases checked: English locale still renders correctly (new keys added to en.ts).\r\n- What you did **not** verify: Other non-English locales.\r\n\r\n## Review Conversations\r\n\r\n- [x] I replied to or resolved every bot review conversation I addressed in this PR.\r\n- [x] I left unresolved only the conversations that still need reviewer or maintainer judgment.\r\n\r\n## Compatibility / Migration\r\n\r\n- Backward compatible? (`Yes`)\r\n- Config/env changes? (`No`)\r\n- Migration needed? (`No`)\r\n- If yes, exact upgrade steps:\r\n\r\n## Risks and Mitigations\r\n\r\nNone.",
